sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Alice
    participant P as Proxy
    participant W as Worker
    participant B as Backend
    participant Bob as Bob
    A->>P: INVITE
    Note over P: HRW select worker-N<br/>insert HMAC Record-Route
    P->>W: INVITE
    W->>B: POST /call/new
    B-->>W: dest · headers · limiters · rules
    Note over W: create Call + aLeg + b-1<br/>flush Redis sidecar<br/>check-and-incr limiters<br/>start no-answer timer 30s
    W->>Bob: INVITE (b-leg)
    P-->>A: 100 Trying
    Bob-->>W: 180 / 200
    W-->>P: 180 / 200
    P-->>A: 180 / 200
    A->>P: ACK
    P->>W: ACK (cookie → N)
    W->>Bob: ACK
